  "texts": [
    "The calibration dataset, with its two channels, relates to EMG data for the arm, forearm, and leg.",
    "The first channel marks the beginning and end of calibration.",
    "The second channel identifies the calibration pose used, either for gforce, involving three specific arm motions, or leg EMG, with two leg motions.",
    "The calibration pose for forearms includes lower arm inward pose and lower arm outward.",
    "And the calibration pose for the arm includes the upper arm inward pose."
  ],
